1. *Vole* da putuje po svetu. (He likes to travel around the world.) 
2. Ona *voli* da čita knjige. (She loves to read books.) 
3. Deca *vole* da igraju igre. (Children like to play games.) 
4. Mi *volimo* da pevamo. (We like to sing.) 
5. Moja sestra *voli* da kuva. (My sister likes to cook.) 
6. On *voli* da pravi drvene figure. (He likes to make wooden figures.)